text: Ðus mycel is þæs landes into Ciltecumbe,<../images/tbar.gif>is ealles an hund hida, mid þam þe þer abutan lið.
Æstuna IIII, æt Afintuna V, & æt Ufintuna V, æt Ticceburnan XXV, to Cylmestuna V, to Stoce V, to Brombrygce, & to Oterburnan V, to Twyfyrde XX, to Ceolbandingtune XX, to Hnutscillingæ V.
